(Getty Images) Image 58 of 58 Beyonce and Jay Z are expecting twins, singer announces on Instagram 1 / 58 Back to Gallery The Bey-hive is going to get two new, tiny additions.
Beyonce posted a photo to Instagram showing off a growing baby bump and announced that she and husband Jay-Z are expecting again, only this time it's twins.
We would like to share our love and happiness. We have been blessed two times over. We are incredibly grateful that our family will be growing by two, and we thank you for your well wishes. - The Carters
A photo posted by Beyoncé (@beyonce) on Feb 1, 2017 at 10:39am PST
A FEW SUGGESTIONS: Popular short, sweet baby names anyone will love
"We would like to share our love and happiness. We have been blessed two times over. We are incredibly grateful that our family will be growing by two, and we thank you for your well wishes," read the post.
While it's not as dramatic as her first pregnancy announcement, leave it to Queen Bey to make her huge announcement using a simple, beautiful photo and still manage to break the Internet.
